---
// Portfolio Section - Projetos em destaque
---

<section id="portfolio" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Header da Seção -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll fade-up">
     
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-black mb-6">
        Projetos em 
        <span class="text-[#00bc61] relative">
          Destaque
          <svg class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-3" viewBox="0 0 200 12" fill="none">
            <path d="M2 10C20 5 40 2 60 3C80 4 100 7 120 4C140 1 160 5 180 8C185 9 190 10 198 10" stroke="#00bc61" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" class="animate-pulse"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-[#A7A9AC] max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Confira alguns dos projetos que desenvolvemos para nossos clientes, 
        cada um com soluções personalizadas e resultados excepcionais.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de Projetos -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8 mb-12">
      
      <!-- Projeto 1: Track by Track -->
      <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 flex flex-col h-full animate-on-scroll fade-up animation-delay-200">
        <div class="h-48 relative overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/trackbytrack.webp" alt="Track by Track" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 group-hover:bg-black/20 transition-colors duration-300"></div>
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#00bc61] text-white text-xs font-semibold rounded-full">
              Web e Mobile App
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 lg:p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 flex items-center">Track by Track</h3>
          <p class="text-[#A7A9AC] mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-grow">
            A plataforma permite que os usuários avaliem músicas individualmente, calculem uma média para o álbum, registrem o histórico de escutas e compartilhem opiniões com a comunidade.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-auto">
            <a href="https://www.trackbytrackapp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#00bc61] font-semibold text-sm hover:text-[#00a555] transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1">
              Ver Projeto →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Projeto 2: Banda Plano Marshall -->
      <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 flex flex-col h-full animate-on-scroll fade-up animation-delay-400">
        <div class="h-48 relative overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/plano-marshall.webp" alt="Banda Plano Marshall" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 group-hover:bg-black/20 transition-colors duration-300"></div>
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#00bc61] text-white text-xs font-semibold rounded-full">
              Landing Page
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 lg:p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 flex items-center">Banda Plano Marshall</h3>
          <p class="text-[#A7A9AC] mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-grow">
            Landing page desenvolvida para a banda Plano Marshall com foco em SEO com foco em ajudar a banda a ter mais visibilidade online e alcançar novos fãs e contratantes.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-auto">
            <a href="https://bandaplanomarshall.com.br" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#00bc61] font-semibold text-sm hover:text-[#00a555] transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1">
              Ver Projeto →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Projeto 3: Conservatório Jauense -->
      <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 flex flex-col h-full animate-on-scroll fade-up animation-delay-600">
        <div class="h-48 relative overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/conservatorio.webp" alt="Conservatório Jauense de Música" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 group-hover:bg-black/20 transition-colors duration-300"></div>
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#00bc61] text-white text-xs font-semibold rounded-full">
              Site Institucional
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 lg:p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 flex items-center">Conservatório Jauense de Música</h3>
          <p class="text-[#A7A9AC] mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-grow">
            Site institucional desenvolvido para o Conservatório Jauense de Música, apresentando informações sobre cursos, professores e eventos musicais.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-auto">
            <button class="text-[#00bc61] font-semibold text-sm hover:text-[#00a555] transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1">
              Ver Detalhes →
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Projeto 4: Portfólio Profissional -->
      <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 flex flex-col h-full animate-on-scroll fade-up animation-delay-800">
        <div class="h-48 relative overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/portfolio-joao.webp" alt="Portfólio Profissional" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40 group-hover:bg-black/20 transition-colors duration-300"></div>
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-[#00bc61] text-white text-xs font-semibold rounded-full">
              Portfólio
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 lg:p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3 flex items-center">Portfólio Profissional</h3>
          <p class="text-[#A7A9AC] mb-4 text-sm leading-relaxed flex-grow">
            Site portfólio moderno desenvolvido para profissional destacar seus trabalhos, habilidades e experiências para recrutadores.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-auto">
              <a href="https://portfoliodev-bkde.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#00bc61] font-semibold text-sm hover:text-[#00a555] transition-colors duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1">
                 Ver Projeto →
             </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
 
    </div>
    
    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll fade-up animation-delay-1000">
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-[#00bc61] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#00a555] hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#00bc61]/25 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <span>Quero Meu Projeto</span>
        <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 

<style>
  /* Animações baseadas em scroll - otimizadas para mobile */
  .animate-on-scroll {
    opacity: 0;
    transition: all 0.4s ease-out;
  }
  
  .animate-on-scroll.fade-up {
    transform: translateY(15px);
  }
  
  .animate-on-scroll.animate-in {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  
  .animation-delay-200 {
    transition-delay: 0.05s;
  }
  
  .animation-delay-400 {
    transition-delay: 0.1s;
  }
  
  .animation-delay-600 {
    transition-delay: 0.15s;
  }
  
  .animation-delay-800 {
    transition-delay: 0.2s;
  }
  
  /* Mobile: animações mais rápidas e sem delays */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .animate-on-scroll {
      transition: all 0.3s ease-out;
    }
    
    .animation-delay-200,
    .animation-delay-400,
    .animation-delay-600,
    .animation-delay-800 {
      transition-delay: 0s !important;
    }
    
    .animate-on-scroll.fade-up {
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
  }
</style> 